Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.51,0:00:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, I'm Dr. David R. Hawkins. I'm a physician, psychiatrist, psychoanalyst, nutritionist.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.41,0:00:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been doing research in the nature of consciousness itself and levels of awareness that the world calls spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.90,0:00:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of this, plus my 35 years of clinical experience, as well as my own personal experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.44,0:00:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,we've derived knowledge that can be extremely useful in alleviating human suffering in all its forms,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.28,0:00:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,many of which I've lived through in my own personal life,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.56,0:00:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and I've been forced to find answers that are outside the field of traditional medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.88,0:00:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,For today, we need to know a little bit more about the nature of consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.37,0:00:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to talk about body, mind, spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.21,0:00:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Holistic Health has used this, body, mind, and spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.59,0:01:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it just a catchphrase? Is it just a slogan?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.97,0:01:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it really mean, body, mind, and spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.13,0:01:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What is spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.63,0:01:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, is that a metaphysical abstraction?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.99,0:01:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a religious dictum?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.83,0:01:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a fantasy of people who are not too well connected with the real world?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.36,0:01:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Just exactly what is this relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.70,0:01:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it will help us and speed up our work with a greater understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.96,0:01:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,To begin with, then, we want to describe how human experience comes about
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.20,0:01:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and sort of look within ourself to see where this fantasy,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.26,0:01:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,this phenomena, actually occurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.55,0:01:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So we want to look at this relationship now between body, mind, and spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.90,0:01:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,from the viewpoint of experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.90,0:01:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll say some things that sound somewhat startling,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.22,0:01:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,such as, to begin with, the fact that the body cannot experience itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.29,0:02:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, that's a startling thought because all of us tend to think of ourselves as being the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.29,0:02:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We tend to think, I am the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.29,0:02:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll quickly see, as we go along, that the body cannot experience itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.99,0:02:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And if we look at it, that this is not so.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.38,0:02:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The body itself is unable to experience itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.38,0:02:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,For instance, my arm cannot experience its own armness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.38,0:02:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,My left arm cannot experience my left armness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.38,0:02:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What is actually going on are sensations coming from the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.50,0:02:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're not experiencing the body anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.50,0:02:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We're experiencing the sensations of the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.79,0:02:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And these sensations of the body
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.79,0:02:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,curiously enough cannot experience themselves either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.79,0:02:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The sensations coming from the arm have to be experienced somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.79,0:02:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And where are they being experienced?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.79,0:02:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They're being experienced in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.11,0:03:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If we do an incision in the brain, for instance,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.11,0:03:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and delete part of the operating mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.11,0:03:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,at least the way it operates on the physical plane,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.11,0:03:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,we fail to experience the opposite side of the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.11,0:03:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This is common, for instance, after strokes, let's say,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.11,0:03:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,where the patient is unable to experience in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.11,0:03:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,even the existence of a portion of their body.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.43,0:03:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So the body cannot be experienced without the sensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.43,0:03:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The sensation can only be experienced in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.30,0:03:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Interestingly enough, mind itself cannot experience itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.30,0:03:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A thought cannot experience its own thoughtness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.30,0:03:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A memory cannot experience its own memoryness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A fantasy doesn't experience its own fantasiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.33,0:03:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That which goes on in mind actually has to be experienced
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.33,0:03:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,in an energy field which is greater than mind itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.33,0:03:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And this energy field we call consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.84,0:04:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It is because of consciousness that you are aware
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.84,0:04:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,of what goes on within mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.13,0:04:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is obviously so,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.13,0:04:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's the very basic reason for anesthesia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.13,0:04:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,When with anesthesia we delete consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.42,0:04:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,then there is no awareness of what is going on in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.42,0:04:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No consciousness, no awareness of mind or body.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.61,0:04:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No mind, no awareness of sensations or body.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.61,0:04:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Consequently, you will notice by some introspection
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.02,0:04:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and watching yourself as you go throughout the day
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.02,0:04:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,that all of your experience is being experienced
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.02,0:04:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,in a more general way than you had realized
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.02,0:04:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,in a more general field of experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.02,0:04:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,which is almost diffuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.02,0:04:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost as though it's everywhere in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.02,0:04:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is within consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.02,0:04:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an interesting little experiment
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.27,0:05:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,to find out where you think you really experience a thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.27,0:05:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If I ask you, where do you think you experience a thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.34,0:05:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,you will say, in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.34,0:05:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That, you see, is the thought about a thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.59,0:05:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You think that you experience a thought there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.59,0:05:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I ask you now to let go of any belief about that,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.59,0:05:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,any belief of where you think you are experiencing a thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.59,0:05:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and instead ask you to point to exactly
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.59,0:05:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,where a thought is being experienced actually,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.59,0:05:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the radical truth of where is the phenomena occurring,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.59,0:05:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,you will find that it is in no particular place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.59,0:05:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thoughtness is occurring.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.59,0:05:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,All you can say is that thoughtness is occurring,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.69,0:05:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and that you have an awareness of the thoughtness,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.69,0:05:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,but you are hard put to exactly put your finger on it
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.69,0:05:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,where it could possibly be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.69,0:05:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No particular place is where it is being experienced
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.85,0:06:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,in sort of a general overall way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It is very necessary for us to know this
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.42,0:06:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,because some of the techniques we will be using
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.42,0:06:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,will be ones that cancel a lot of these belief systems
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.42,0:06:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,that are at the very basis of human suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.42,0:06:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Consciousness itself, then, is like a movie screen
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.42,0:06:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,upon which that which is changing is experienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If you notice, if you look at it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.38,0:06:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,you will see that all experience is experience of change.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.38,0:06:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the coming and going, the waning and ebbing,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.38,0:06:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the flux, the movement that you are experiencing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.38,0:06:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason we can experience that which changes
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.51,0:06:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,is because it is being experienced
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.51,0:06:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,from a background of that which in itself is unchanging.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.51,0:06:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It is because the movie screen is standing still
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,that we can see the movement of the movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.51,0:06:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So what is experienced, then, is change,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.54,0:07:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and where it is experienced is consciousness itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.54,0:07:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,which has no exact location.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.54,0:07:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We are going to be talking about fear
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.54,0:07:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,as a level of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.54,0:07:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,to be addressed where it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.54,0:07:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,not in its expression and its extension into the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.54,0:07:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,fear of this, fear of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,not trying to handle it on the level of the particular,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,but handling it as a level of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.54,0:07:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,becoming aware of that which we are,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.54,0:07:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,which is greater than the fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.54,0:07:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,learning to disidentify with the emotion,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.54,0:07:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,so that I am not that,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.54,0:07:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I am that in which that is being experienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.54,0:07:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It becomes a small thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.54,0:07:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,a phenomenon going on with that greater experience
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.54,0:07:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,which I experience as myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.54,0:07:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that which I really am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.96,0:07:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So we are going to be talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.96,0:07:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the letting go of fear and the techniques.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.12,0:08:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the biggest obstacles to fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.12,0:08:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the difficulty in handling it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.12,0:08:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,is the fear of fear itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.12,0:08:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we will be describing a technique
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.12,0:08:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,which disappears the fear of fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.12,0:08:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you are no longer afraid of fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.12,0:08:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,it becomes a very simple matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.28,0:08:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it about fear?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.28,0:08:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It is your fear of it, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.34,0:08:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The person is afraid of the fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.34,0:08:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,afraid of the fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.73,0:08:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,just as the person going to the dentist
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.73,0:08:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,is afraid of the pain, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.89,0:08:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So it is that initial fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.89,0:08:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and when we begin to look at the nature of fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.89,0:08:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,we can see that the number of fears are endless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.89,0:08:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The number of fears are endless,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.43,0:08:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore people become victim,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.43,0:08:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,they become convinced
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.43,0:08:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,that the source of fear is outside of themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.43,0:08:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think the source of fear is outside of yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.59,0:09:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,there is frankly very little you can do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.59,0:09:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, there is really nothing you can do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.59,0:09:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What you can do is try and jump at this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.10,0:09:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,but because the source is always outside of yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.10,0:09:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,you will always be the victim of fear
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.10,0:09:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,until you begin to realize
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.10,0:09:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,that it is the pre-set conditions within you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.10,0:09:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,that you are the source of the fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.10,0:09:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,which you then project onto the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.10,0:09:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and of course you are sure that you see it out there
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.10,0:09:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,because you just projected it out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.90,0:09:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,When we look at fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.90,0:09:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,we see how all-pervasive it can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If you realize that fear is a level of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.90,0:09:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,then you realize that from that level of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.90,0:09:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,fear can be attached to everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.96,0:09:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to overcome particular fears
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.96,0:09:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,may have a certain limited value,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.96,0:09:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but it doesn't change you as a fearful person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.96,0:09:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't change you as a fearful personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.96,0:09:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't change you as a fearful human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.96,0:10:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The fear of a specific fear may be clinically valuable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.76,0:10:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It may be practically useful in your life,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.76,0:10:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,but it doesn't alter who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.76,0:10:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Today we are going to be looking more at who you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.76,0:10:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,how the conditions of this can be changed,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.76,0:10:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,so that you never more feel like a small self
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.76,0:10:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,who is powerless
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and at the effect of the victimhood of fear itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.76,0:10:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, fear can be like a prefix
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.98,0:10:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,which gets attached to anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are in an energy field,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.17,0:10:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and we are going to be talking today about energy fields,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.17,0:10:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,we are going to be talking about this map of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.17,0:10:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,which we have on the blackboard,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.17,0:10:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and which we have been using throughout this series.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.17,0:10:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Throughout the series we have been talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,levels of consciousness here,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.17,0:10:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and you will see fear right about here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.17,0:10:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We are going to be talking about fear as a level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.17,0:11:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That this level of consciousness here,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.17,0:11:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,these are the lower levels of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.17,0:11:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,these are the higher ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.17,0:11:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We are going to be talking about fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.17,0:11:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We see that it is a negative emotion
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.17,0:11:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,by the direction of the arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.17,0:11:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We see its relative power,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.17,0:11:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,because this is a mathematical model.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,In the mathematical model,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.17,0:11:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,we have been able to calibrate the relative energies
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.17,0:11:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,of these different fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.17,0:11:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, starting from 30, 50, 75.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.17,0:11:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,As we go up from the negative emotions
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.17,0:11:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,into the positive emotions,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.17,0:11:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,we see that their actual power,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.17,0:11:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,from the viewpoint of physics,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.17,0:11:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,actually increases.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.17,0:11:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So we are going to be dealing today with this fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.20,0:11:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,A negative energy field,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.74,0:11:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,which calibrates on a relative scale,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.74,0:11:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,where death would be zero
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.74,0:11:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and enlightenment would be 600,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.74,0:11:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,love would be 500,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.74,0:11:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,we see that fear comes out at 100.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.74,0:11:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We are going to be talking about this energy field then,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.10,0:12:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and you begin to realize that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.16,0:12:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,being fearful then can attach to anything
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.16,0:12:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and everything in your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.16,0:12:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There is nothing in your total experience
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.42,0:12:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,as a human being
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.42,0:12:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to which fear cannot be attached.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.42,0:12:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You love your mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,up comes the fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.42,0:12:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,what if you lose her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.42,0:12:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You love your body,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.42,0:12:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,up comes the fear of death, sickness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.42,0:12:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You love money,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.42,0:12:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,up comes the fear of loss,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.42,0:12:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,or of being accused of being greedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.96,0:12:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what you think of,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.96,0:12:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,fear can be attached to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.96,0:12:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You love your automobile,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.96,0:12:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,up comes the fear of an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.96,0:12:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A fearful person then attaches the fear to everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.96,0:12:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So everything that comes into the mind
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.96,0:12:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,is coming into an energy field of fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.96,0:12:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore gets colored with fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.96,0:12:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,A fear of life itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.22,0:12:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And as the song goes,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.22,0:12:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,afraid of living and afraid of dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.22,0:12:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Afraid of living and afraid of dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.22,0:12:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.22,0:12:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,this energy field has now contaminated everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.22,0:13:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So if I am the source of that energy field then,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.28,0:13:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,all of my experience comes into the field of fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.28,0:13:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and everything in my life becomes fearful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.28,0:13:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The future is fearful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.28,0:13:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Old age, getting older.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.28,0:13:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going to happen to the body?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.28,0:13:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going to happen to my finances?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.28,0:13:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going to happen to my relationships?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.28,0:13:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going to happen to my family?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.28,0:13:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going to happen to my car?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.28,0:13:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going to happen to my bank account?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.28,0:13:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going to happen to my country?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.28,0:13:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going to happen to the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.28,0:13:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And so people who get into a global fear
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,will tell you about the fears of nuclear annihilation,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.28,0:13:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the endless fears of intergalactic wars.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.28,0:13:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, the expansion of the fear
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.28,0:13:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't change the fact that it is still just fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.28,0:13:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Glamorizing it, making it sound dramatic,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.14,0:13:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't change that it's just fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.14,0:13:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The fear of intergalactic war and human demolition
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.14,0:13:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and the expiration of the human race
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.14,0:13:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,is no different than the fear of the child,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.14,0:13:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the child's fear of the dark,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.14,0:13:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,his fear that a dog might bite him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.14,0:14:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What's characteristic of all of it
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.14,0:14:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,is an energy field called fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.14,0:14:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear of what is really immaterial.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.14,0:14:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're going to have to learn to look away from the thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.14,0:14:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and look instead to the feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.14,0:14:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Look below the feeling to the energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.14,0:14:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,out of which this feeling is coming
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.14,0:14:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and learn how to handle this energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.14,0:14:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,When we do this, we lose our fear of fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.88,0:14:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And as we lose our fear of fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.88,0:14:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,we begin to learn how to handle fear directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.88,0:14:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Handling fear directly is extremely simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.98,0:14:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It is an extremely simple thing to handle
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.98,0:14:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,once we're familiar with some rather simple techniques.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.98,0:14:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the world pretty much runs you with fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.98,0:14:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,does it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Because your life is pretty much run by fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.98,0:14:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you've learned a way to not get cornered by fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.98,0:14:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you're beginning to transcend the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.98,0:14:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're beginning to transcend being victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.98,0:14:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Because really, what can the world do in its threat?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.98,0:14:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How can the world threaten you except through fear?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.98,0:15:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,To cut off your bank account,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.98,0:15:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,to get audited,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.98,0:15:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,to run away from you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.98,0:15:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,to leave you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.98,0:15:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,to fire you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.98,0:15:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The gun at your head is always the same gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.98,0:15:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always the gun of fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.98,0:15:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The fear of losing a part of your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.30,0:15:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The endless fears, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.30,0:15:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no end to the number of fears.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.30,0:15:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no end to the number of fears.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.30,0:15:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But there is an end to fearfulness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.30,0:15:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There is an end to being victim of fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.30,0:15:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There is an end to being afraid of fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.29,0:15:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll learn today how to lose our fear of fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.29,0:15:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,how to enjoy the process,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,how to really start feeling good about yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,when you realize that you are no longer the small victim,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.29,0:15:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,the worm,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.29,0:15:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,who is at the effect of this all-pervasive fearfulness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.29,0:15:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's not fear but this energy field of fearfulness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.29,0:15:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And we begin to see that we are in control of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.29,0:15:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We are the source of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.29,0:16:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,See, I'm the source of my fearfulness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.93,0:16:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we all know, in a different mood,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.93,0:16:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,the same thing is no longer fearful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.93,0:16:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.99,0:16:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a thing that you're afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.99,0:16:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You say, I am afraid of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.99,0:16:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But when you're accompanied by somebody else,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,when you're in a different mood,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.99,0:16:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,when you're in a humorous mood
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.99,0:16:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and having a good time laughing,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.22,0:16:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,now that thing no longer engenders fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.22,0:16:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So the source of fear is not in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.22,0:16:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no way of overcoming one's fear of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no way the world can be controlled
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.22,0:16:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,to overcome your fears.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.22,0:16:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And society's endless efforts
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.22,0:16:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,to end your fears by changing society,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.22,0:16:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,by changing the laws,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.22,0:16:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,by changing the rules,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.22,0:16:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,will not end the fear
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.22,0:16:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,because fearfulness is within you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.22,0:16:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,One is the event itself
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.22,0:16:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and secondly, how you feel about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.47,0:16:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So having more police might make you feel better,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.47,0:17:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,but in fact, where are the police going to be
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.47,0:17:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,while your apartment is being robbed?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.47,0:17:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,At the other end of town, naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.47,0:17:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So therefore, our handling the fear
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.14,0:17:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,is really up to ourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.14,0:17:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes out of our willingness
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.14,0:17:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,to own that we are the source of that fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.14,0:17:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That fear is occurring within our own consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.14,0:17:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore we want to address it
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.14,0:17:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,where it is actually being experienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.30,0:17:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Most people experience fear
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.30,0:17:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,in a sort of a physical way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.30,0:17:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So that the first thing we want to do
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.30,0:17:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,about a fearful experience
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.30,0:17:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,is to eliminate paying any attention to thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.91,0:17:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason is that a fearful feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,will engender literally millions of thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.91,0:17:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no end to fearful thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.91,0:17:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,because they are coming out of an energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.91,0:17:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,of fear itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.91,0:17:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,which generates an endless series of thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.04,0:17:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Clinically speaking,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.04,0:17:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,handling the specific thoughts themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.04,0:18:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,has a limited value
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.04,0:18:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and that fearfulness
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.04,0:18:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,merely generates more thoughts later on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.62,0:18:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So we want a technique that will handle fear itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.18,0:18:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You might just picture something
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.18,0:18:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,fearful in your life,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.18,0:18:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,something fearful that you expect may happen
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.18,0:18:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,or which has happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.18,0:18:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,or you can just fantasy a fearful experience
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.18,0:18:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,such as being tied to the railroad track
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.18,0:18:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and a locomotive is bearing down on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.18,0:18:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,When you look at what is being experienced
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.27,0:18:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll see when you look past the thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.27,0:18:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,that it's being experienced first of all in the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.27,0:18:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What you'll notice is
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.27,0:18:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe a tenseness in the stomach muscles,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.27,0:18:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,a queasy feeling in the stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.27,0:18:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,A shakiness in the arms and the legs
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.27,0:18:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,or a dryness in the mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.27,0:18:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people have cramps,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.27,0:18:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,intestinal cramps or intestinal phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.34,0:18:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever it is in your own case
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.34,0:19:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,you look within yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.34,0:19:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,to see what is actually being experienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.34,0:19:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,See radical truth means
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.34,0:19:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,what's being experienced actually
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.34,0:19:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,not what you are thinking about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.34,0:19:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,not the thoughts about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.34,0:19:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the concepts that you're projecting onto it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.34,0:19:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You're projecting onto the experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.34,0:19:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the labeling,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.34,0:19:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the putting of a word on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.34,0:19:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,but what are you literally experiencing
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.34,0:19:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,within yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.94,0:19:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The technique then is to let go resisting
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.94,0:19:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the experiencing
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.94,0:19:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,of what is literally being experienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.94,0:19:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go resisting the dryness in the mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.94,0:19:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let it be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.94,0:19:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.94,0:19:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go resisting
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.94,0:19:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the flip-flop feeling in the stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.94,0:19:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go resisting the trembling
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.94,0:19:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,in your arms and legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.94,0:19:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,When you do this you're focused you see
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.94,0:19:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,away from thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.94,0:19:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,onto what is being experienced
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.94,0:19:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and you let go,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.94,0:19:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,fully let go,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.94,0:19:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,surrender to
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.94,0:19:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,being with those sensations.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.74,0:20:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The letting go then is like
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.74,0:20:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,the willow tree in the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.74,0:20:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming from
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.74,0:20:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the Taoism of China let us say,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.96,0:20:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the ancient wisdom of China
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.96,0:20:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,which states that the oak tree
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.50,0:20:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,which resists the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.50,0:20:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,is susceptible to breaking
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.50,0:20:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and the willow tree
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.50,0:20:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,which bends with the wind survives.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.50,0:20:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And so like the willow tree
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.50,0:20:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,we bend with the incoming experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.50,0:20:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We let it be.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.50,0:20:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We blend with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.50,0:20:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We welcome it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.50,0:20:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We say let's have more of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.50,0:20:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,As you do that you'll discover
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.50,0:20:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,much to your surprise
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.50,0:20:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,that there is a limited amount
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.50,0:20:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,of that sensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.50,0:20:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as though
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.60,0:20:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the amount of fear that we have
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.60,0:20:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,is limited in quantity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.60,0:20:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How can this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.70,0:20:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as though
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.02,0:20:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,this fear is like a pressure tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.02,0:20:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,All the suppressed fear
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.02,0:20:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,that we've had
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.02,0:20:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,throughout our lifetime,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.02,0:20:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,starting in our childhood,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.02,0:20:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,all that fear that we couldn't
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.02,0:21:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,allow ourselves to experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.02,0:21:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,couldn't allow ourselves to express,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.02,0:21:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,weren't allowed to express,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.02,0:21:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,weren't allowed to have that emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.21,0:21:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,To the man let's say
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.21,0:21:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,in the service,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.21,0:21:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,he wasn't allowed to express
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.21,0:21:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,that fearfulness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.21,0:21:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It was thought to be unmanly,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.21,0:21:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe cowardice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.21,0:21:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And so that fear gets suppressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.21,0:21:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It gets repressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.21,0:21:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It gets pushed down out of awareness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Fears have come up by the thousands
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.21,0:21:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,in our lifetime
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.21,0:21:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,of which we were even unaware.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.21,0:21:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You see the fear comes up
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.21,0:21:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and unwittingly you brace your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.21,0:21:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That fear just got pushed out of awareness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.27,0:21:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Or you drum your fingers on the desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.27,0:21:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening is the fear
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.27,0:21:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,is so quickly suppressed
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.27,0:21:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,that you don't even realize
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.27,0:21:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,that it was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.27,0:21:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,As the years go by,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.94,0:21:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the accumulated energy of this fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.94,0:21:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the energy is what we're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.94,0:21:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy behind this fear
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.94,0:21:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,increases in pressure
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.94,0:21:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and when it reaches a certain point,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.94,0:21:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,as though you reached a red line
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.94,0:22:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,on the needle of the dial,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.94,0:22:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,what happens is this pressure now
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.94,0:22:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,of this fearfulness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.94,0:22:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,begins to express itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.94,0:22:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It spills out, spills over
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.94,0:22:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,into our experience
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.94,0:22:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and begins to color it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.74,0:22:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't examine it,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.74,0:22:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,we think that this fear
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.74,0:22:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,is coming from the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.74,0:22:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We blame the world for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.74,0:22:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We think that there is a fearful experience
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.74,0:22:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,happening out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.74,0:22:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Little do we realize
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.74,0:22:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,that it is merely our own fearfulness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.74,0:22:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,being projected out into the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.74,0:22:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So we own that this source of the fear then
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.74,0:22:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,is our own accumulated fearfulness.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.74,0:22:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And we start to welcome
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.74,0:22:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and look forward to the opportunities
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.74,0:22:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,to allow this fearfulness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.74,0:22:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.83,0:22:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the sensations
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.83,0:22:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and the inner experience of fear itself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.83,0:22:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,remains the same
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.83,0:22:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter what we think we're afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.83,0:22:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If somebody holds a shotgun
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.09,0:23:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,to your heart and says,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.70,0:23:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,give me all your money,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.70,0:23:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,what are you going to experience?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.70,0:23:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to experience dry mouth,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.70,0:23:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,weakness in the knees,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.70,0:23:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and that old familiar flippy-foppy feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.70,0:23:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,in the stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.70,0:23:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If an enemy tank rolls up to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.89,0:23:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,knocks it over,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.89,0:23:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and they rotate the barrel of the gun
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.89,0:23:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and put it right at your forehead,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.89,0:23:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,what are you going to experience?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.89,0:23:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to experience
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.89,0:23:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,exactly the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.89,0:23:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The same thing if somebody
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.89,0:23:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,holds a mouse over your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.89,0:23:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to experience
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.89,0:23:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,a dryness in your mouth,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.89,0:23:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,a queasiness in your stomach,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.89,0:23:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,cramps in the intestine,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.89,0:23:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and that jiggly feeling in your muscles.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.89,0:23:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,All that you ever have to handle
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.89,0:23:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,is those sensations.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.89,0:23:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,See, with this fearfulness,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.89,0:23:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,see, with experiencing this technique,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.89,0:23:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll learn that all you ever have to handle
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.89,0:23:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,is what you're experiencing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.89,0:23:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,within consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.89,0:23:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether it's localized within the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.89,0:23:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,or whether more sophisticated
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.02,0:23:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,after you've meditated
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.02,0:24:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and worked with this technique,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.02,0:24:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll notice that this experience
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.02,0:24:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,is happening in a general and diffused
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.02,0:24:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,sort of everywhere-ness.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.02,0:24:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The phenomena of the queasy muscles,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.02,0:24:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the flip-flop in the stomach,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.02,0:24:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the dry mouth,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.02,0:24:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,is being experienced
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.02,0:24:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,in sort of a vague,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.02,0:24:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,diffuse everywhere-ness,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.02,0:24:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and you just let go resisting that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.02,0:24:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You just allow the experience
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.02,0:24:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,to be there without resisting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.02,0:24:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're focused on that,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.02,0:24:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the fear begins to diminish.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.02,0:24:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,For one thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.02,0:24:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,you're no longer paying attention
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.02,0:24:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,to the thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.02,0:24:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, the thoughts themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.02,0:24:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,are engendering further fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.02,0:24:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're very busy with this technique,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.02,0:24:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,just letting go, resisting the fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.02,0:24:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,you're now focused
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.02,0:24:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,on the energy field itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.02,0:24:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Behind this fearfulness
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.02,0:24:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,is an energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.02,0:24:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And what you're doing
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.02,0:24:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,is letting go the resisting
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.02,0:24:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,of the releasing,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.02,0:24:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,progressive releasing
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.02,0:24:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and discharge of this energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.02,0:25:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,By doing this,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.69,0:25:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,you lose your fear of fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.69,0:25:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear is no longer an awesome terror
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.87,0:25:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,that awakens you in the middle of the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.87,0:25:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing but
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.87,0:25:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,an inner emotional experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.87,0:25:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The sensations of which
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.87,0:25:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,can be easily handled.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.87,0:25:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask yourself, truly,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.87,0:25:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,can you handle a dry mouth?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.87,0:25:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.87,0:25:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Doing research and experimenting
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.87,0:25:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,with this particular technique,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.29,0:25:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I had an experience
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.29,0:25:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,that I want to share with you
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.29,0:25:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,because it demonstrates
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.29,0:25:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,one of the principles
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.29,0:25:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,that we are describing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.29,0:25:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I had had a lifetime fear of heights.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.29,0:25:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So severe, for instance,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.29,0:25:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,that when I went to visit
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.29,0:25:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,the Grand Canyon for the first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.29,0:25:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I literally couldn't get
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.29,0:25:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,within 100 feet of the edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.29,0:25:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And it created that panicky feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.29,0:25:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,when I even saw somebody else
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.29,0:25:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,get near the edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.29,0:25:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I was using this technique
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.96,0:25:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,whenever I could
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.96,0:25:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and enjoying the progress
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.96,0:25:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I was making with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.96,0:25:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just somehow never got around
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.96,0:25:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to working on my fear of heights.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.96,0:26:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was working on fear
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.96,0:26:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,from all its other origins
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.96,0:26:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,within my experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.96,0:26:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And the next time I went back
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.02,0:26:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,to the Grand Canyon
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.02,0:26:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,was about a year and a half
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.02,0:26:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,or two years later.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.02,0:26:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And much to my amazement,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.02,0:26:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I could walk up within
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.02,0:26:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,about 20 feet of the edge
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.02,0:26:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,before this tight feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.02,0:26:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,occurred in the stomach again.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.02,0:26:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And I continued to utilize this technique
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.12,0:26:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,over the next year or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.12,0:26:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And again, about two years later,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.12,0:26:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I went back there
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.12,0:26:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,with some members of my family
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.12,0:26:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,to revisit the canyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.12,0:26:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And much to my surprise,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.12,0:26:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I could walk right up
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.12,0:26:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,to the very edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.12,0:26:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, I could dangle
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.12,0:26:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,my feet over the edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.12,0:26:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't say I was happy about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.12,0:26:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,but I did it the impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.12,0:26:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I was really so pleased.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.12,0:26:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But what it demonstrated
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.12,0:26:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,was the principle
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.12,0:26:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,that what I had been releasing
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.12,0:26:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,was that accumulated pressure,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.12,0:26:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the accumulated energy
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.12,0:26:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,of all that fear from a lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.12,0:26:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And like a pressure tank,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.12,0:26:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,as it released itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.12,0:26:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,now there was less and less
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.12,0:26:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,to spill over into life's experiences.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.12,0:27:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The letting go then of resisting
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.12,0:27:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,is so effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.12,0:27:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And why is it effective?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.12,0:27:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we see that resistance
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.12,0:27:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,traps us into a certain
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.12,0:27:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,state of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.12,0:27:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And resistance is right
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.12,0:27:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.12,0:27:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not written on the board,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.12,0:27:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,but when we calibrate it,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.12,0:27:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,it is a negative energy
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.12,0:27:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,at about 150.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.18,0:27:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And the important thing
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.18,0:27:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,over here, you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.18,0:27:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,is the important thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.18,0:27:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.18,0:27:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the important thing
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.18,0:27:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,on this line
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.57,0:27:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,of this energy field here
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.57,0:27:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,is that one is trapped by that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.57,0:27:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,One is trapped by this.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.57,0:27:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,One can't get beyond it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.57,0:27:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,One becomes victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.57,0:27:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So one becomes the victim
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.57,0:27:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,of their own fears
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.57,0:27:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,so long as they own,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.57,0:27:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,don't own that they are
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.57,0:27:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the source of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.57,0:27:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So long as we rationalize
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.57,0:27:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and try to say
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.57,0:27:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,that the source of the fear
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.57,0:27:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,is out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.57,0:27:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,so long as we think
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.57,0:27:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the source of the fear
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.57,0:27:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,is out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.57,0:27:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,we cannot overcome it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.57,0:27:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I begin to own
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.57,0:28:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,that I am the experiencer,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.57,0:28:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the one that sets up
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.57,0:28:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the way in which
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.57,0:28:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I experience things,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.57,0:28:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,now I become the one
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.57,0:28:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,who is master of the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.57,0:28:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,My soul's self-esteem
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.57,0:28:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes affected.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.57,0:28:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I am no longer the one
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.57,0:28:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,who is the victim
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.57,0:28:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,or subject to fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.57,0:28:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I am something else
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.57,0:28:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,other than the fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.57,0:28:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, fear is nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.57,0:28:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,but an experience
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.57,0:28:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,in consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.57,0:28:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and I don't give it reality anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.60,0:28:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,by labeling it
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.60,0:28:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and by filling in fear of what.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.60,0:28:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The what-ness I'm sure
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.60,0:28:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,you see by now is endless.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.60,0:28:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Fearfulness is attached
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.40,0:28:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,to everything in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.40,0:28:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,by a fearful person.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.40,0:28:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Changing the world
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.40,0:28:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,will not handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.40,0:28:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A person can be terribly afraid
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.40,0:28:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,in a very safe situation
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.40,0:28:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and afraid not at all
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.40,0:28:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,in a very dangerous situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.40,0:29:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,one which hypothetically
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.40,0:29:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,is dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.40,0:29:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So we have two situations,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.50,0:29:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,let us say.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.50,0:29:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,One is being mugged.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.50,0:29:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.62,0:29:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we have the fear
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.62,0:29:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,of being mugged.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.62,0:29:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That is something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.62,0:29:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The fear of being mugged
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.62,0:29:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,is not the same as being mugged.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.62,0:29:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It is quite possible
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.62,0:29:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,to have very unfortunate circumstances
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.62,0:29:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,happen in one's life
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.62,0:29:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and not experience fear at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.62,0:29:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, to experience
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.62,0:29:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,that one is the witness
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.62,0:29:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,of the phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.62,0:29:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a thing happened to me
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.62,0:29:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,in my own life
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.62,0:29:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,when I walked into
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.62,0:29:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,a very large-sized rattlesnake
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.62,0:29:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,on the top of a nearby mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.62,0:29:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.62,0:29:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,As I went to step into this cabin,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.62,0:29:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,much to my surprise,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.62,0:29:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,here was a giant rattlesnake
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.29,0:29:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,coiled up there
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.29,0:29:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and as I lifted my foot
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.29,0:29:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,to step on him,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.29,0:29:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,his head snapped back
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.29,0:29:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and his tongue blew out
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.29,0:29:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and he just was ready
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.29,0:29:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and poised to strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.29,0:29:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So in that instant,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.32,0:30:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,in that instant,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.32,0:30:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,there was a flash
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.63,0:30:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,of fearful thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.63,0:30:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the thought of
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.63,0:30:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I could take a club and hit it,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.63,0:30:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I could run,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.63,0:30:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I could yell for help,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.63,0:30:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't have a gun
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.63,0:30:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,but somebody might shoot it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.63,0:30:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, all the
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.63,0:30:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,automatic self-protective thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.76,0:30:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that social consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.76,0:30:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,has programmed us with.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.76,0:30:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Happily and luckily for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.02,0:30:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,or I probably wouldn't be here
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.02,0:30:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,giving you this talk today,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.02,0:30:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I had learned this technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.02,0:30:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, instantly I realized
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.02,0:30:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,that my life, frankly,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.02,0:30:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,depended on my utilization
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.02,0:30:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,of this technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.50,0:30:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And so what I did instead
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.50,0:30:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,is I automatically
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.50,0:30:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,went into this exact technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.50,0:30:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I automatically let go,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.50,0:30:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,wanting to do anything about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.50,0:30:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,wanting to handle anything about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.50,0:30:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,wanting to change anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.50,0:30:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, I went into my inner self
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.50,0:30:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and I just allowed
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.50,0:30:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the inner experience
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.50,0:30:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,to release itself
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.50,0:30:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,without any resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.50,0:30:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.50,0:31:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I welcomed more of it
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.50,0:31:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,because somehow
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.50,0:31:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,when you really get into the
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.50,0:31:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,experience of your own
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.50,0:31:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,inner consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.50,0:31:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you really see that your survival
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.50,0:31:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,really depends on this
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.50,0:31:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and it has all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.56,0:31:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So I saw that my
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.56,0:31:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,survival really depended
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.56,0:31:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,on the excellence
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.56,0:31:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,with which I let go
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.56,0:31:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and surrendered and released
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.56,0:31:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and let go resisting the experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.56,0:31:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,As I did,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.59,0:31:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the fearful thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.59,0:31:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,instantly disappeared
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.66,0:31:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and I felt like a profound
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.66,0:31:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,state of peace
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.66,0:31:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,settle on the snake and myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.66,0:31:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like I became the witness,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.07,0:31:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,not the witness confined
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.07,0:31:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,to this body,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.07,0:31:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,but the witness in consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.07,0:31:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,which seemed to have no dimension.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.07,0:31:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And this
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.17,0:31:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,formless dimension
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.17,0:31:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,was then the experiencer
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.17,0:31:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,of the presence
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.17,0:31:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,of a state of peacefulness.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.17,0:31:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This profound state of peacefulness
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.17,0:31:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,was of such power
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.17,0:31:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,that it prevailed
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.17,0:31:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,over the consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.17,0:31:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,of both the snake
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.17,0:32:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and the personality
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.17,0:32:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,of this person speaking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.17,0:32:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And so,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.17,0:32:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,the snake looked at me
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.17,0:32:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,interestedly,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.17,0:32:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,having not seen a human being,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.17,0:32:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think in his whole life,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.17,0:32:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,much less a foot away.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.17,0:32:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And I looked at the rattlesnake
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.46,0:32:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,with great curiosity
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.46,0:32:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and thought of him as brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.46,0:32:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The two of us were included
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.46,0:32:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,in the oneness of this space
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.46,0:32:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,of our own beingness together
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.46,0:32:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,in a state of extreme intimacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.46,0:32:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And out of it came
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.46,0:32:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,sort of an inner joyfulness
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.46,0:32:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and I like felt
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.46,0:32:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the love for the snake arise.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.46,0:32:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It arises out of the field,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.46,0:32:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.46,0:32:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,once the fear is removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.80,0:32:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If we look at our
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.80,0:32:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,scale of consciousness over here
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.80,0:32:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that we've been talking about,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.80,0:32:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,we can track what had happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.80,0:32:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You see,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.80,0:32:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,we track what had happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.80,0:32:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.80,0:32:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,which has a negative energy field,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.80,0:32:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,which the snake
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.80,0:32:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,would have instantly picked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.80,0:32:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He instantly would have picked up
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.80,0:32:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,or instantly would have picked up anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.80,0:32:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,My desire,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.80,0:32:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,let's say,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.80,0:32:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,to strike at him
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.80,0:33:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and his responses
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.80,0:33:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,through his energy system
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.80,0:33:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,are so fast,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.80,0:33:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the strike would have happened
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.80,0:33:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,before I could have moved
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.80,0:33:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,my shin out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.80,0:33:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.80,0:33:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,because of the severe threat
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.80,0:33:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,of the circumstance
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.80,0:33:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and the circumstances,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.80,0:33:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.80,0:33:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.80,0:33:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.80,0:33:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,did I ever let go?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.80,0:33:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And I jumped right through
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.80,0:33:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the willingness to let go,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.80,0:33:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,right through the acceptance,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.80,0:33:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,right to the love,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.80,0:33:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,right to the joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.80,0:33:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,right to a state
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.80,0:33:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,of profound peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.80,0:33:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I would say
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.80,0:33:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,if I calibrated
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.80,0:33:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.80,0:33:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,of that experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.80,0:33:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,it would probably come out
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.80,0:33:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,around 599,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.80,0:33:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe 600.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.80,0:33:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Because there was
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.80,0:33:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the feeling of a presence,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.80,0:33:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,an infinite presence
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.80,0:33:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,whose essential nature
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.80,0:33:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,is one of peace
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.80,0:33:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and whose power
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.80,0:33:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,is infinite
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.80,0:33:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and that controlled
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.80,0:33:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the whole experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.80,0:33:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And thus,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.80,0:33:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,both the snake
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.80,0:33:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and myself
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.80,0:33:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,transcended fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.80,0:33:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The falsity
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.80,0:33:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,of another one
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.80,0:33:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,of the mind's belief systems
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.80,0:33:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that we have to learn
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.80,0:33:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,to let go of.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.80,0:33:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The idea
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.02,0:33:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,that fear
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.02,0:34:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,is the source
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.02,0:34:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,of our safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.02,0:34:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll notice
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.04,0:34:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,that the mind
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.04,0:34:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,sort of worships fear
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.04,0:34:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,as though it's
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.04,0:34:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,some kind of a demi-god.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.04,0:34:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And the mind
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.04,0:34:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,has sort of a program
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.04,0:34:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,that says,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.04,0:34:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the reason
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.14,0:34:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm alive
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.14,0:34:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,is due to
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.14,0:34:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,my fears.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.14,0:34:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.46,0:34:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I allow fears
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.46,0:34:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,to decide
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.19,0:34:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,what I'm going
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.19,0:34:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,to do
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.19,0:34:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,that I'm alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.19,0:34:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A little introspection
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.19,0:34:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,will show you
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.26,0:34:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that this belief system
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.26,0:34:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,is going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.26,0:34:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The person says,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.26,0:34:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,well,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.15,0:34:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,if I wasn't afraid
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.15,0:34:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,of being poor
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.15,0:34:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,in my old age,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.15,0:34:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't get insurance,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.15,0:34:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.15,0:34:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If I wasn't afraid
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.15,0:34:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,of an automobile accident,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.15,0:34:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't drive safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.15,0:34:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And so,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.15,0:34:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the person begins
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.82,0:34:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,to ascribe
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.82,0:34:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the source
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.82,0:34:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,of their aliveness,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.82,0:34:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the source
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.82,0:34:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,of their life,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.82,0:34:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the god of their life,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.82,0:34:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,is fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.82,0:34:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They really begin
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.82,0:34:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,to worship fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.08,0:34:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we see
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.08,0:34:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,from the example
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.08,0:34:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,that I just described
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.08,0:34:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,that the opposite
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.08,0:34:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.14,0:34:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What ensures
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.14,0:34:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,our survival
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.14,0:35:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,is the absence
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.14,0:35:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,of fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.21,0:35:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And you might say
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.21,0:35:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,that we have
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.21,0:35:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,managed to survive
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.21,0:35:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,in spite
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.21,0:35:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,of our fears
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.21,0:35:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,but not because
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.21,0:35:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.04,0:35:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,As you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.04,0:35:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,we can make decisions
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.04,0:35:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,based on
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.04,0:35:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,rational choice,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.04,0:35:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,based on
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.04,0:35:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,our knowingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.04,0:35:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,on our knowledge,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.04,0:35:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,based on our value,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.04,0:35:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,coming from
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.04,0:35:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,the beingness
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.04,0:35:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,of that which
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.04,0:35:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,we really are
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.04,0:35:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,without fear
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.04,0:35:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,entering the picture
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.04,0:35:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.00,0:35:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All day long
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.00,0:35:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,we make decisions
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.00,0:35:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that are just
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.00,0:35:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,based on
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.00,0:35:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,our awareness
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.00,0:35:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,of reality
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.00,0:35:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,with no fear
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.00,0:35:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,particularly
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.00,0:35:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.00,0:35:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear is not
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.35,0:35:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.35,0:35:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The idea
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.35,0:35:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,that fear
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.35,0:35:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,is good
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.35,0:35:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.35,0:35:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,that it's
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.35,0:35:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,valuable,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.35,0:35:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,that it has
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.35,0:35:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,all kinds
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.35,0:35:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,of mysterious
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.35,0:35:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,values,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.35,0:35:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,people will
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.35,0:35:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,look back
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.35,0:35:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and rationalize
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.35,0:35:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,how fear
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.35,0:35:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,got them
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.35,0:35:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,to do this
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.35,0:35:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and fear
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.35,0:35:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,got them
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.35,0:35:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.35,0:35:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.35,0:35:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I can say
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.35,0:35:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,it's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.35,0:36:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad they didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.35,0:36:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,do it out of
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.35,0:36:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,love for themselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.35,0:36:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,out of love
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.35,0:36:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,for their fellow
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.35,0:36:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,human beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.35,0:36:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad they didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.35,0:36:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,do it out of
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.35,0:36:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,love for life
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.58,0:36:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.58,0:36:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,love for their
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.58,0:36:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,own aliveness,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.58,0:36:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,love for their
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.58,0:36:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,body.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.58,0:36:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not do
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.58,0:36:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,this?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.58,0:36:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not keep
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.58,0:36:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,it healthy and
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.58,0:36:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,happy because
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.58,0:36:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,you love it
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.58,0:36:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and value it,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.58,0:36:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,not because
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.58,0:36:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,you're afraid
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.58,0:36:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,of a heart
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.58,0:36:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,attack or
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.58,0:36:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,afraid of
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.58,0:36:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,something.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.56,0:36:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it out of
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.56,0:36:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,valuing it
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.56,0:36:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and loving
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.56,0:36:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.56,0:36:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ways to let
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.56,0:36:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,go more
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.56,0:36:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,of this fear
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.56,0:36:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,will describe
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.14,0:36:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,another technique
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.14,0:36:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,which I call
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.14,0:36:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the worst
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.14,0:36:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,scenario.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.14,0:36:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You see,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.14,0:36:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,if you follow
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.14,0:36:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,fear as you
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.14,0:36:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,will see,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.14,0:36:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,if you ask
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.14,0:36:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.14,0:36:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,are you afraid
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.14,0:36:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,of driving
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.14,0:36:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,your car?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.14,0:36:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I might
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.14,0:36:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,have an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.14,0:36:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, why are
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.14,0:36:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,you afraid of
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.14,0:36:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,an accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.14,0:36:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, because
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.14,0:36:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,then I might
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.14,0:36:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,get injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.14,0:36:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what if
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.14,0:37:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,you got injured?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.14,0:37:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then I
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.14,0:37:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,might suffer
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.26,0:37:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,pain, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.26,0:37:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And you'll find
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.64,0:37:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that every fear
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.64,0:37:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,ultimately will
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.64,0:37:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,lead you to
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.64,0:37:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the fear of
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.64,0:37:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,death.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.64,0:37:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear of the
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.64,0:37:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,body's dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.64,0:37:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll lead you
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.64,0:37:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,to fears of
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.64,0:37:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,whether other
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.64,0:37:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,people like
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.64,0:37:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.64,0:37:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What fear does
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.64,0:37:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that bring up
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.64,0:37:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and what fear
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.64,0:37:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,is the basis
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.64,0:37:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.64,0:37:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We finally get
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.64,0:37:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,to the worst
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.64,0:37:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,scenario.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.64,0:37:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The worst
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.64,0:37:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,scenario,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.64,0:37:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,let's say your
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.64,0:37:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,financial fears,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.64,0:37:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,are that you
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.64,0:37:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,will totally
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.64,0:37:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,run out of
